OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778756575
OL,3,CFootage shows new progress in major
OL,4,Coperation to clear huge waste dump
OL,6,FWATCH: Drone footage shows the
OL,7,Fprogress being made by the Environment
OL,8,FAgency as it continues the lengthy
OL,9,Fclear-up.
OL,11,FNew footage of a major operation to
OL,12,Fremove a huge fly-tip in Oxfordshire
OL,13,Fshows the clean-up is underway, but
OL,14,Ffar from complete.
OL,16,FDrone footage, captured by ITV
OL,17,FMeridian, shows the progress being
OL,18,Fmade by the Environment Agency in its
OL,19,Fmission to clear 21,000 tonnes of
OL,20,Fillegally dumped waste.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
