OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778756575
OL,3,CFootage shows new progress in major
OL,4,Coperation to clear huge waste dump
OL,6,FDiggers and lorries have begun the
OL,7,Fpainstaking process of collecting and
OL,8,Fferrying the rubbish away from the
OL,9,Fsite, near the River Cherwell and A34
OL,10,Fin Kidlington.
OL,12,FHowever, the scale of the dump, which
OL,13,Fis nearly 12 metres high in places,
OL,14,Fmeans it will be months before the
OL,15,Fclean-up is complete.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
