FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778756575
OL,3,CFootage shows new progress in major
OL,4,Coperation to clear huge waste dump
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency is not
OL,7,Ftechnically funded to clear illegal
OL,8,Fwaste dumps, but stepped in to remove
OL,9,Fthe rubbish after warnings from
OL,10,FOxfordshire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,11,Ffound the site posed a serious fire
OL,12,Fhazard.
OL,14,FHaving started the clean-up in April,
OL,15,Fthe agency estimates it will take
OL,16,Fanother five months to finish. The
OL,17,Ftotal cost is expected to be around #7
OL,18,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778756575
OL,3,CFootage shows new progress in major
OL,4,Coperation to clear huge waste dump
OL,6,FThe Environment Agency is hoping to
OL,7,Frecoup those costs in court, however,
OL,8,Fby seizing money from the criminals
OL,9,Fwho illegally dumped the waste.
OL,11,FTo date, four men have been arrested
OL,12,Fas part of the agency's criminal
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,FThey include: a 39-year-old from
OL,16,FGuildford who was held in November; a
OL,17,F69-year-old from Andover, and a 54-
OL,18,Fyear-old in Slough who were arrested
OL,19,Fin January; and a 52-year-old from
OL,20,FAshford who was detained in February.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
