OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778756575
OL,3,CFootage shows new progress in major
OL,4,Coperation to clear huge waste dump
OL,6,FThe dump was first visited by the
OL,7,FEnvironment Agency in July 2025. Since
OL,8,Fthen, environmental campaigners have
OL,9,Fraised concerned about the possible
OL,10,Fleaching of chemicals and other
OL,11,Fharmful material into the River
OL,12,FCherwell.
OL,14,FThe Environment Agency says there is
OL,15,Fno evidence of any pollution of the
OL,16,Friver, however.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
