FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1778756575
OL,3,CFootage shows new progress in major
OL,4,Coperation to clear huge waste dump
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Environment
OL,7,FAgency said: "Regular monitoring has
OL,8,Ffound no evidence the River Cherwell
OL,9,Fhas been polluted by waste, which is
OL,10,Fheld back from the river by barriers
OL,11,Fand sandbags.
OL,13,F"We share the widespread anger about
OL,14,Fthe waste dumped at Kidlington by
OL,15,Fshameless criminals.
OL,17,FThey added: "Four men arrested as part
OL,18,Fof our fast-moving criminal
OL,19,Finvestigation to find those
OL,20,Fresponsible remain part of our
OL,21,Fcriminal investigation."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
